 {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "840716281119571", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57574720_840716291119570_6338633741422904364_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mJrcCgQiecgQ7kNvgFc02pQ&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAy-hSPKv_pMd2IehdVPOfTXEopU0J_4Z6eflYzeq6bGQ&oe=66FBC8DB"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "488412717275961", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974525_488412720609294_7458364120634917665_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EUGwhsliPfsQ7kNvgH4DT05&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA8DhR7e-gxsUEJLcHvDpNpYvHyKNjRMTt_DGJ9Co9CqA&oe=66FBF251"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "427144199756021", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223486_427144203089354_4369279694658394896_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LyGIaWDH_l8Q7kNvgEY-IIH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA9CrhH64Vj8XmPk3CM7Y55hGRLgBv4yyo9lgYkgRg1RQ&oe=66FBD10F"}]}, "id": "1062082695522073", "locale": "it_IT", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "422140790868918", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_422140794202251_1640211663921085746_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jTECmvSRc-kQ7kNvgGj2ydt&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCn9DCr8wgaAdpYld8gY601vIYi2ewQghPzaV771KejGQ&oe=66FBD92A"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "468838062692515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984464_468838066025848_9209980070403449565_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=d9_MPW528aIQ7kNvgGoH4_b&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBWIaARRjEa6VQJ2kwb9WsZdgni47YgTIYi9198c9X4iw&oe=66FBD50C"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "481654227990009", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031353_481654234656675_3114596455803752280_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CSxLbt4Qd3YQ7kNvgHvJ2YM&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBY9vbcOqAwxuprgXxH5-C_UpdzMY2otN6IJGJThx6B-A&oe=66FBD390"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "3889565187981667", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_3889565191315000_5528783709779854295_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Esy-2X7YgigQ7kNvgFVG11s&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYApQO9dINW_qin9ART_l1S20YaQ-Km8UG1DVCZWFB7MtA&oe=66FBD324"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "867384681933118", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003244_867384685266451_2340853765823917163_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ysUwCqEOMzcQ7kNvgG5Pq21&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCchE-1B3--pBf7xVFvNkO3capLzXViZ0uUd-Af1naqIw&oe=66FBD745"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "999991165259980", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476756_999991168593313_5483195490028886346_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bFacez_6CacQ7kNvgFLtZ9N&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBqhGH_SAigsj4_vQQHZiWPmkNZNCbC0MXEQSBE3vTbUw&oe=66FBE4B1"}, "display_name": "Safari Cellulare", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellulare** \u00e8 un'applicazione di realt\u00e0 virtuale innovativa che trasforma l'apprendimento della **biologia cellulare** in un'avventura emozionante. Progettata per **studenti, educatori e appassionati di scienza**, questa app ti permette di esplorare una **cellula animale in 3D** come mai prima d'ora. Attraverso un'interfaccia immersiva, puoi navigare tra le diverse strutture cellulari, come **il nucleo, i mitocondri e il reticolo endoplasmatico**, scoprendone le funzioni e l'importanza.\n\nOgni componente della cellula \u00e8 rappresentato con dettagli straordinari, permettendoti di osservare e comprendere i processi biologici complessi in modo visivamente accattivante. **L'intelligenza artificiale integrata** \u00e8 a tua disposizione per rispondere a qualsiasi domanda tu possa avere durante l'esplorazione, fornendo spiegazioni chiare e dettagliate.\n\nSafari Cellulare non \u00e8 solo un'esperienza educativa passiva; include una serie di **mini giochi interattivi** progettati per consolidare le tue conoscenze in modo divertente e coinvolgente. Attraverso **sfide e quiz**, puoi mettere alla prova la tua comprensione dei concetti biologici, rendendo l'apprendimento un processo attivo e stimolante.\n\nPerfetta per l'uso in ambito educativo o come strumento di autoapprendimento, Safari Cellulare offre un modo nuovo e innovativo per esplorare il mondo microscopico della cellula animale. Con **grafica di alta qualit\u00e0** e un'**esperienza utente intuitiva**, questa app trasforma lo studio della biologia in un'avventura indimenticabile.", "short_description": "Scopri l'affascinante mondo della cellula animale con Safari Cellulare, l'app VR educativa che ti permette di esplorare le strutture cellulari in 3D. Attraverso mini giochi interattivi e un'intelligenza artificiale avanzata, apprendi concetti scientifici divertendoti. Ideale per studenti e appassionati di biologia, questa esperienza immersiva rende l'apprendimento un'avventura entusiasmante."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "7830788620364802", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974477_7830788637031467_2492816240902607915_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=t7szHMlxRWkQ7kNvgH1QVus&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBKeTE7QikHKHNM0xBNVRHbYTRTM-el9ucKOzDAoeCB5g&oe=66FBEA2C"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "1994643360958356", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462955_1994643364291689_8067620305322327621_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xC7Ut4TUaJcQ7kNvgFhXnmv&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAc4TS57ba8L7oCTAdxWusbu4uzV9GtKR0uXRMkHvSURw&oe=66FBCF8F"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "1749848195756080", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003273_1749848199089413_6210488408238311147_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=prweGGHAfUQQ7kNvgFlSew7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAdbaq0Ok84VLqJf4i65sAsibu_1cV8VdVvhvI3P00YbA&oe=66FBCB86"}, {"file_name": "Hero Cover.png", "id": "1019117086331658", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974548_1019117092998324_1164601898764144918_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=H9APNyuNixUQ7kNvgH_j28N&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDzll9vErdCW23t0ce6zedHO4hqeI08uAYUgvxanMM72w&oe=66FBE5A8"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "872400761490753", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031450_872400768157419_814239069343010651_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MZfqrj_PKfYQ7kNvgGCcxck&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCBOHJtiL2LKRwoPySh3e25gRpp97fpVpyg4MeLSBKW-Q&oe=66FBC9A3"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "513806047726163", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982645_513806051059496_4223857969464332917_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=W4JIncFBwCAQ7kNvgHK5dC9&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDe7bAuDgftF3eS2ScWgex3ArI9POF9ktTt3OO6yAIfWg&oe=66FBDF0B"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "493094060118611", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031398_493094063451944_436248626179243058_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MNUM3P4MnbQQ7kNvgGGuNSG&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAVl7JpqJeWNwvk-pGcCWjs5_mn1qouW2V8nHPb7XL3zA&oe=66FBE399"}]}, "id": "1030659978605601", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "2759662717526847", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036623_2759662720860180_2489395151907338724_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2I4pOrkOZbsQ7kNvgFZCqjN&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBxrcd3f815Rck8nlYumhw3UeGdMNazQLPxafeGV-bALQ&oe=66FBF572"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "2251639125188099", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AyfIpCR5a1wQ7kNvgF3iiZm&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBUV4gAGoFRUAfARiFUg5N-usxQ2nW4YAkODr0r5E3b0A&oe=66FBE2A9"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "473243412277688", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984439_473243418944354_2938823070153890993_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=B6x2GHwzSb0Q7kNvgFMGloC&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC2ETTdAhFuXw0MoTroBIxP9CLIY8XzOu6Bp4TipF8tBw&oe=66FBCB37"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "1543351499921825", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974887_1543351503255158_348442130487521407_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Pl15FKcpazEQ7kNvgEPCSjU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAEyegtXlMkORSxbm_Ms2NHhwB16uvORD3mdjpziA8Pug&oe=66FBD146"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "912383657378781", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031432_912383660712114_2572436446715478623_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LW00h_fY18IQ7kNvgFFPcfW&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDcBiHLj9hwDaz8dRkT-9-cp4cJyes6Q7zYTS-zl70C0g&oe=66FBF07A"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "3748813912049179", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031311_3748813915382512_2166423531006939259_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gxA6OADvxmYQ7kNvgHpJeX7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD1--8vaALJXL46VIau5Fhuczo0y82juqYTtEG0dzmY1g&oe=66FBCCCD"}, "display_name": "Cellular Safari", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellular** is an innovative virtual reality app that turns learning about **cellular biology** into an exciting adventure. Designed for **students, educators and science enthusiasts**, this app allows you to explore an **animal cell in 3D** like never before. Through an immersive interface, you can navigate through different cell structures, such as **the nucleus, mitochondria, and endoplasmic reticulum**, discovering their functions and importance.\n\nEach component of the cell is represented in stunning detail, allowing you to observe and understand complex biological processes in a visually engaging way. **Integrated artificial intelligence** is at your disposal to answer any questions you may have while exploring, providing clear and detailed explanations.\n\nCellular Safari is not just a passive educational experience; it includes a series of **mini interactive games** designed to consolidate your knowledge in a fun and engaging way. Through **challenges and quizzes**, you can test your understanding of biological concepts, making learning an active and stimulating process.\n\nPerfect for use in education or as a self-study tool, Cellular Safari offers a new and innovative way to explore the microscopic world of the animal cell. With **high-quality graphics** and an **intuitive user experience**, this app turns the study of biology into an unforgettable adventure.", "short_description": "Discover the fascinating world of the animal cell with Cell Safari, the educational VR app that lets you explore cellular structures in 3D. Through interactive mini-games and advanced artificial intelligence, learn scientific concepts while having fun. Ideal for students and biology enthusiasts, this immersive experience makes learning an exciting adventure."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "7934545376658361", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.